import sys

n, a, b = map(int, sys.stdin.readline().split())

x, y = [], []

for i in range(n):
    x.append(int(sys.stdin.readline().split()[0]))
    y.append(int(sys.stdin.readline().split()[1]))

x.sort(reverse=True)
y.sort(reverse=True)

ans = 0

for i in range(n):
    for j in range(i + 1, n):
        if x[i] + x[j] <= a and y[i] + y[j] <= b:
            ans = max(ans, x[i] * y[i] + x[j] * y[j])

print(ans)
